FBIS3-41994 "jptnd004___94013" JPRS-TND-94-004 Document Type:JPRS Document Title:PROLIFERATION ISSUES 11 February 1994 LATIN AMERICA CUBA Study on Radiation Status Noted FL1401151894 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1255 GMT 14 Jan 94 FL1401151894 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Report by National News Agency correspondent Nieves Toledo] [Text] According to the results of a study carried out by specialists from the Radiation Protection and Hygiene Center [Centro de Proteccion e Higiene de las Radiaciones] and the provincial delegations of the Executive Secretariat for Nuclear Affairs, Cuba has optimal radiological environmental conditions, favorable for any kind of human activity.
